{"tid":656871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人慣性嘔吐？","createTime":"2018-05-07T15:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T02:53:49.000Z","uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7601b149294dda7de93cfb9313f263b019eae6b0","tid":656871,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T15:07:25.000Z","msg":"差唔多兩星期一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係突然嘔 嘔之前有先兆<br />\n頭痛/視覺受阻 有陣白光遮住視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後格一陣就嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔食生野 但都成日嘔<br />\n老母話睇黎要照胃鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇又無結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇醫生又淨係識比止嘔藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人好似我咁？"},{"pid":"7ad0093e14cf32e1e43ff980245c8ca91a25f980","tid":656871,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"你不如諗下食左乜野做左乜野之後會嘔"},{"pid":"25015d1fb1c49719e230172cb1741ff8265c6434","tid":656871,"uid":36049,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"係咪你照鏡咋😂😂😂😂"},{"pid":"da7f936e13aff988e5482f9a0a669dbf25f66f4e","tid":656871,"uid":36045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"壓力大 同埋 唔夠瞓<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔係醫生"},{"pid":"b4386c90aa99b4df3b05a689e357851f47798e7d","tid":656871,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ad0093e14cf32e1e43ff980245c8ca91a25f980","tid":656871,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"你不如諗下食左乜野做左乜野之後會嘔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T15:17:38.000Z","msg":"食野好單一<br />\n一係米線 一係炒粉麵飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做就無規律 <b